HEADWORD: Reis Effendi
<hw>Reis` Ef*fen"di</hw> <pr>(r?s` ?f*f?n"d?)</pr>. <ety>[See 2d
<er>Reis</er>, and <er>Effendi</er>.]</ety> <def>A title formerly given
to one of the chief Turkish officers of state. He was chancellor of the
empire, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

